WEBVTT

00:05:00.222 --> 00:05:02.021
Ni pia vile nisivyovijua

00:05:02.045 --> 00:05:05.439
vilivyonileta karibu na kila mtu
anaenizunguka.

00:05:06.549 --> 00:05:08.549
Kwa Novemba nane mfululizo, hivi karibuni,

00:05:08.573 --> 00:05:13.001
nimesafiri kila mwaka kupitia
Japan na Dalai Lama.

00:05:14.001 --> 00:05:17.101
Na kitu ambacho alikuwa anasema kila siku

00:05:17.125 --> 00:05:20.672
ambacho kilionekana kuwapa watu
suluhisho na tumaini

00:05:20.696 --> 00:05:22.754
ilikuwa ni "sijui."

00:05:24.325 --> 00:05:26.202
"Nini kitatokea Tibet?"

00:05:27.226 --> 00:05:30.206
"Lini tutapata amani duniani?"